{"results":[{"aya":"043","id":4457,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"櫕（木+苦）木的果实，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"044","id":4458,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"确是罪人的食品，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"045","id":4459,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"象油脚样在他们的腹中沸腾，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"046","id":4460,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"象开水一样地沸腾。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"047","id":4461,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"（主说）你们捉住他，然后，把他拖入火狱中，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"048","id":4462,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"然后，再把沸水的刑罚倾注在他的头上！","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"049","id":4463,"locale":"zh","sura":"044","text":"你尝试吧！你确是显赫的，确是尊贵的！","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":9,"previousPage":"/zh/s044-6.json","nextPage":"/zh/s044-8.json"}}